'''Gereza ya Gikondo''' cyangwa '''Gereza yo mu mujyi wa Kigali''' ni iherereye i [[Kigali]], mu [[Rwanda]] . Yubatswe mu myaka ya za 1930, yari igamije kubamo imfungwa nkeya cyane. Nyuma ya [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|jenoside yo]] mu Rwanda, umubare wariyongereye ugera ku 50.000 kuko umubare munini w'abagororwa bari abajenosideri. Benshi bazanywe mu nkiko za Gacaca kugira ngo baburanishwe kubera ibyaha by'intambara  na jenocide ariko bakaguma muri gereza.

Komite mpuzamahanga ya Croix-Rouge yagize uruhare runini mu gusuzuma aho bafungiye, imibereho yabo ndetse no muzindi  gereza zo mu Rwanda, muri jenocide byarushijeho kuba bibi nubwo byagaragaye ko hari iterambere mbere y'intambara.

Mu Kwakira 1999, ICRC yashyikirije raporo y'ibanga abayobozi bakuru bo mu Rwanda. Nyuma y’imishyikirano, CICR yongeye kunoza itangwa ry’ibiribwa, umutungo n’imiti ku mfungwa z’abasivili, isana gereza kandi itanga ibikoresho byo kwifashisha muri gereza. 

